What diet has worked best for you? 
</P>
<P>
Responses gathered by Lauren Walden (El Modena), Elaine Ust (La Habra), Shelly 
Insheiwhe (Los Amigos), Candace Purvis (Mater Dei), Brooke Lyons (St. 
Margaret's), Claudine Ko (University) and Heather Lee (Villa Park). 
</P>
