<HEADLINE>
<P>
VIDEO DISCOVERY: MORE VIDEOS: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By GUILLERMO TORRES 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Fandango" (1985), directed by Kevin Reynolds, 91 minutes. Rated PG. Critics 
panned this, one of Kevin Costner's first movies, because they said it went 
nowhere. 
</P>
<P>
But who says a movie has to go anywhere? This tale of five graduating Texas 
college students contemplating their futures is poignant and adventurous. 
GUILLERMO TORRES 
</P>
