<P>
Beyond 'Ghost': Whoopi Goldberg signed an exclusive agreement Tuesday to star 
in Paramount Pictures' feature films, it was announced by the studio's Motion 
Picture Group. Goldberg's relationship with Paramount began when she starred as 
a psychic in the studio's recent blockbuster, "Ghost." CLAUDIA PUIG 
