Davidson in the now-defunct New York Herald Tribune. Bruce Davidson; Photo, 
Right, author Tom Wolfe and, LARRY DAVIS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, below, 
part of the gang today: Gary Watkins, foreground, Jackie Haddad Hellingson, 
center, and Vicki Bellardo with her son Gilbert in stroller. BRUCE K. HUFF / 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, Ari Davis, foreground, leads Ty Hellingson and others 
down the "sewer line," the unofficial path to the Windansea Beach in La Jolla. 
They represent the 1990 version of the old Pump House Gang. DAVE GATLEY / Los 
