cheerleader whose face was slashed in an August attack she said was racially 
motivated, breaks down in court while recounting her near-fatal injury. ; 
Photo, Ralph Jones describes how defendant allegedly threw shard of glass that 
injured girl. ; Photo, Amber Jefferson, right, talks with Louis Jones during 
court recess. AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
