Grant Elementary in Santa Ana in pilot program. ; Photo, Dr. Paul Qaqundah 
listens to chest of Roberto Remigio at Grant Elementary School after telling 
him to take a deep breath. MARK BOSTER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
