<TEXT>
<P>
Santa Claws is coming: Does Fluffy want a new rawhide chew bone for Christmas? 
</P>
<P>
She can bark her wishes to Santa this weekend at Laguna Hills Mall. 
</P>
<P>
A group of veterinarians will dress up as Santa Claus -- or, as they say, Santa 
Claws -- and pose for photographs with shoppers and their pets at the mall. 
Proceeds from the photo sales will benefit the San Clemente Animal Shelter. 
