<TEXT>
<P>
Luisito Espinosa of the Philippines retained his World Boxing Assn. 
bantamweight title today with a unanimous decision over challenger Taloengsak 
Sitbobey of Thailand. 
</P>
<P>
The taller, rangy Filipino dominated the 12-round bout from start to finish, 
knocking down and bloodying the Thai, but failed to put him away. The judges 
scored it 117-112, 115-113 and 116-114. 
